snippet.textDisplay: In case nobody knew or already said, this game was originally supposed to be Terminator but somehow Sunsoft lost the rights, but still had the finished game. So they simply changed the story, sprites and the intro music. Now that I've seen the Terminator Nes game I can honestly say that all of us Terminator fans got screwed over. This is an awesome game with an awesome soundtrack. Terminator they failed you!!
snippet.textOriginal: In case nobody knew or already said, this game was originally supposed to be Terminator but somehow Sunsoft lost the rights, but still had the finished game. So they simply changed the story, sprites and the intro music. Now that I've seen the Terminator Nes game I can honestly say that all of us Terminator fans got screwed over. This is an awesome game with an awesome soundtrack. Terminator they failed you!!
